Package gobblin.dataset

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Dataset
    Interface representing a dataset.
    DatasetsFinder<T extends Dataset>
    Finds Datasets in the file system.
    FileSystemDataset
    Dataset in a file system, which can be characterized by a root Path.
    IterableDatasetFinder<T extends Dataset>
    A DatasetsFinder that can return the Datasets as an Iterator.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IterableDatasetFinderImpl<T extends Dataset>
    Wraps a DatasetsFinder into an IterableDatasetFinder.
